                     <interp inst="t17980418-41-defend325" type="age" value="36"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , was again indicted for <rs id="t17980418-41-off209" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980418-41-off209" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980418-41-off209" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17980418-41-cd210" type="crimeDate">20th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980418-41-off209 t17980418-41-cd210"></join>, four silver table-spoons, value 40s. two silver tea-spoons, value 5s. and a pair of silver sugar-tongs, value 6s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17980418-41-victim327" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Wilson
                        <interp inst="t17980418-41-victim327" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
